accessibility claims. This talk focuses on

00:01:24.960 --> 00:01:29.759
the following: how to use accessibility
standards for authoring tools to help

00:01:29.759 --> 00:01:36.640
answer the detailed questions:
WCAG 2.0 and 2.1, US and EU public

00:01:36.640 --> 00:01:41.600
